<Page x:Class="text_quest.Page9"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:local="clr-namespace:text_quest"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="500" d:DesignWidth="800"
      Title="Page9">

    <Grid VerticalAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Center">
        <Grid>
            <Border BorderBrush="Black" BorderThickness="1" Background="#FF87CEEB" CornerRadius="10" Width="540" Height="500"/>
        </Grid>
        <StackPanel>
            <Grid>
                <TextBox x:Name="pageThreeTxt" 
                         Height="280" Width="500"
                         Margin="18" 
                         Background="AliceBlue" 
                         FontSize="25" Padding="25" 
                         TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow" 
                         AcceptsReturn="True" 
                         VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" 
                         IsReadOnly="True" 
                         BorderBrush="Black">
                    Due to the recent events at your new job you realize that you are insanely tired and decide to take a day off to have some rest.
During your lunch you are browsing a web page with an interesting article about the extinction of a rare species of one-eyed parrots Gigachades, when suddenly some program starts downloading without your consent. What do you do?

                    <TextBox.Resources>
                        <Style TargetType="{x:Type Border}">
                            <Setter Property="Width" Value="500"/>
                            <Setter Property="Height" Value="280"/>
                            <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="3"/>
                        </Style>
                    </TextBox.Resources>
                </TextBox>
            </Grid>
            <Button Click="nextFromOne" Background="BlueViolet" Margin="5">
                <TextBlock FontSize="15" Foreground="White">Allow the program to install thinking it is a normal update</TextBlock>
                <Button.Resources>
                    <Style TargetType="Border">
                        <Setter Property="Width" Value="500"/>
                        <Setter Property="Height" Value="45"/>
                        <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="10"/>
                    </Style>
                </Button.Resources>
            </Button>
            <Button Click="nextFromTwo" Background="BlueViolet" Margin="5">
                <TextBlock FontSize="15" Foreground="White">Interrupt the download and check the system for viruses</TextBlock>
                <Button.Resources>
                    <Style TargetType="Border">
                        <Setter Property="Width" Value="500"/>
                        <Setter Property="Height" Value="45"/>
                        <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="10"/>
                    </Style>
                </Button.Resources>
            </Button>
            <Button Click="nextFromThree" Background="BlueViolet" Margin="5">
                <TextBlock FontSize="15" Foreground="White" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center">Ignore the event and continue reading the article without paying attention to it</TextBlock>
                <Button.Resources>
                    <Style TargetType="Border">
                        <Setter Property="Width" Value="500"/>
                        <Setter Property="Height" Value="45"/>
                        <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="10"/>
                    </Style>
                </Button.Resources>
            </Button>
        </StackPanel>
        <Grid>
            <TextBox x:Name="tbTime" Margin="27,24,0,0" Background="LightPink" Width="20" Height="20" HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Top" BorderBrush="Black">
                <TextBox.Resources>
                    <Style TargetType="Border">
                        <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="10"/>
                    </Style>
                </TextBox.Resources>
            </TextBox>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Page>
